The Landessanitätsdirektion Wien and the medical crisis team of the city of Vienna regularly inform about the current case numbers and other key figures for the COVID-19 virus: As of Sunday, 26 July 2020, 8.00 o'clock, 4,840 (+ 60) positive tests are confirmed in Vienna.
